💗Are you game on for some healthy Middle Eastern Vegetarian food made using the freshest ingredients?💗 Do check out @fillapitasg 👌🏼They offer a range of dips/sides such as hummus, fava beans, labna cheese, falafels as well as pita sandwiches and platter ⁣
⁣
Swipe left to check out their menu❤️ They are available for takeaways and delivery.⁣
⁣
For delivery👇🏼⁣
💗Minimum order of $20⁣
💗$2.50 delivery fee per order⁣
💗Free delivery above $40⁣
⁣
Thank you @fillapitasg for the yummies!⁣
